Privacy Policy
1. Introduction
Welcome to [Your App Name]. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our application, which includes advertising and in-app purchases.
2. Information We Collect
Personal Information
: We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or payment details directly. However, third-party services used for advertisements and in-app purchases may collect such information.
Usage Data
: We collect non-personal information about your interactions with the app, such as usage patterns, session duration, and feature usage. This data helps us improve the app and provide a better user experience.
3. How We Use Your Information
To Provide and Improve Our Services
: We use collected data to ensure the app functions correctly, enhance performance, and develop new features.
For Advertising
: We use third-party ad networks to display ads within the app. These networks may collect information about your activity to serve relevant ads.
For In-App Purchases
: When you make a purchase within the app, payment processing is handled by third-party services. We do not store payment information but may collect data related to your purchase history to manage your subscription.
4. Third-Party Services
Our app uses third-party services for advertising and payment processing. These services have their own privacy policies, and we recommend reviewing them:
Advertising
: We use [e.g., Google AdMob, Facebook Audience Network]. These networks may collect information about your device and usage to deliver targeted ads.
Payment Processing
: In-app purchases are processed by [e.g., Apple App Store, Google Play Store]. Payment information is handled by these platforms according to their privacy policies.
5. Data Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy in the app and updating the effective date. Your continued use of the app after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
7. Contact Us
